headline.print_headline: Boehner to Face College Professor in US House Bid
headline.main: Boehner to Face College Professor in US House Bid

lead_paragraph: House Speaker John Boehner defeated two tea party challengers Tuesday in his bid for a 13th term in Congress, brushing aside some GOP discontent over his leadership in Washington.
